node.text: Happy Birthday 🎁 to my Princess Ariana👸 You are everything a father could ask for and more. I am beyond lucky to able to have your smile brighten up my life everyday. You will always be my little 😇 and I promise to make every Birthday better and better! #Happy3rdBirthday
